# Cursor (WSL) + Android Studio (Windows) development

- **Single** editable copy: **`/home/…`** paths under WSL in Cursor; Android Studio on Windows must open the **same** folder via **`\\wsl.localhost\…`** or **`\\wsl$\…`** (`docs/dev/setup.md`).
- **`local.properties`** out of git: Linux **`sdk.dir`** for `./gradlew` under WSL, or **Windows** SDK path (escape `\`) for Gradle sync launched by Studio from Windows per your config.
- Keep line endings consistent (**LF**). Avoid two large concurrent Gradle syncs from Cursor + Studio on the same root.
